videos.description: Jared Harper lobs it up to Anfernee McLemore who slams it home, then immediately off the inbounds Harper turns a steal into two more.
videos.headline: Auburn kicks things off with dunk, steal and score

videos.description: RJ Barrett elevates through the Auburn defender and finishes through contact for the Duke bucket.
videos.headline: Barrett drives left for and-1 finish

videos.description: Duke freshman Tre Jones drives baseline and hits a baseline shot before the buzzer.
videos.headline: Jones makes circus shot to beat shot clock

videos.description: Jared Harper gets his layup blocked off the backboard by Marques Bolden.
videos.headline: Bolden pins Auburn attempt at the basket

videos.description: Jared Harper tries going coast-to-coast before halftime but Zion Williamson shuts the door.
videos.headline: Williamson blocks Harper before halftime buzzer

videos.description: Zion Williamson runs the floor and tosses an alley-oop to RJ Barrett for a dunk.
videos.headline: Williamson lobs to Barrett to start 2nd half

videos.description: RJ Barrett gets out ahead of the pack and flushes a windmill dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB One-Play (Barrett throws down fastbreak windmill) 2018/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barrett throws down fast-break windmill

videos.description: Auburn gives Cam Reddish too much space as he knocks down a long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Reddish pulls up for deep 3

videos.description: Marques Bolden comes up with a block on defense, then runs the floor for an alley-oop.
videos.headline: Bolden blocks, runs the floor and finishes alley-oop
